@layout('layout-docs')

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto docs-content">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
    <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-violet-100 dark:bg-violet-500/20 text-violet-700 dark:text-violet-400 text-xs font-semibold">Plugin</span>
    <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 text-xs font-semibold">Auth</span>
  </div>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Socialite — OAuth Authentication</h1>
  <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-8">Social authentication for Nimbus. Sign in with GitHub, Google, Discord, Apple — and more — using a clean, unified API inspired by Laravel Socialite.</p>

  <!-- ── Overview ── -->
  <h2 id="overview" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
    <span class="text-amber-500">§</span> Overview
  </h2>
  <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4">Socialite handles the entire OAuth2 flow — redirect, callback, user profile retrieval — so you can add social login with just a few lines of code. It ships as a first-party Nimbus plugin with built-in support for:</p>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-6">
    <div class="text-center p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-1.5">
      <div class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482C19.138 20.197 22 16.44 22 12.017 22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">GitHub</div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-1.5">
      <div class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
